stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Booting
  Booting --> Ready: session opened
  Booting --> Failed: auth or workspace error

  Ready --> Sending: user sends message
  Sending --> WaitingAgent: 202 accepted
  Sending --> Failed: network or validation error

  WaitingAgent --> Ready: assistant_final or error event
  WaitingAgent --> Stopping: stop requested
  Stopping --> Ready: stopped or no_active_job

  Ready --> Resetting: reset requested
  WaitingAgent --> Resetting: reset requested
  Resetting --> Ready: new session_id

  Failed --> Sending: retry same client_message_id
  Failed --> Ready: user edits or cancels
